# Cron alternative — single checker pass every 5 minutes, exits between runs.
# Simpler than systemd; fine for plain (non-browser) watches. Install with:
#   crontab -e     (then paste the line below, fixing the path)
#
# Logs land in checker.log next to the script.

*/5 * * * * cd /opt/poke-checker && /usr/bin/node checker.mjs --once >> checker.log 2>&1

# Pre-order config on a gentler 10-minute cadence:
# */10 * * * * cd /opt/poke-checker && /usr/bin/node checker.mjs --once --config preorders.json >> checker.log 2>&1
